Another post about building Story Stains, the previous one can be found at &ldquo;Story Stains: Frontend&rdquo;.
Enums Enums are a way of having multiple options programmatically, when a Boolean (true or false) isn&rsquo;t expressive enough. Think traffic lights: Red, Orange, Green, Http Status Codes: Unauthorized, Not Found, OK,&hellip;, and Countries: Germany, Poland, Great Britain, England? UK?&hellip;
Some things seem obviously able to fit into an Enum data type, until they don&rsquo;t.
